Package: spectrolab
Type: Package
Title: Essential functions to process spectral data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: Anna K. Schweiger
Maintainer: Anna K. Schweiger <anna.k.schweiger@gmail.com>
Description: Essential functions to process data from portable
    spectrometers: list, read, plot data, perform jump correction,
    vector normalisation, smoothing at the sensor overlap regions,
    filter out bad measurements.
    Currently only for SVC (Spectral Vista Inc.).
